    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmotiles turns planet terraforming experience into a minimalist strategy game. It offers a simple  game mechanic. At the same time, provides enough depth for challenging and rewarding experience for seekers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/fe6af0268e213c17ddc572f6bf8b265e.avif?t=1769252121\" width=616 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to place blocks on planet. A block is a group of tiles with a same biome. Placing a block is scored  based on surrounding biomes in non linear fashion! One more tile will increase score significantly with number of tiles. At a time you will get certain choices of blocks to pick few. Find sequence of block placement to maximize score for current shuffle of blocks or take a risk to increase score for next shuffle of blocks.<br><br>Once you score enough points, a new land expansion is unlocked to continue terraforming. However, if you run out of empty tiles to place blocks, the game ends. This is the time when you check your score on the leaderboard and start again. <br><br>Each planet comes with own puzzle with varying land mass, shuffle sizes and biome types. Planets are generated every start to provide new experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/2dc121a3480dfa1a3762af14839be560.avif?t=1769252121\" width=616 height=77 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Cosmotiles offers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique mix of strategy and puzzle mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High replay value - every start is different</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic placement to beat the highscore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No time pressure, play at your own pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for playing now and then</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Cosmotiles does <strong>not</strong> offer</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4X Strategy   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource Management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat &amp; Violence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cinematic story</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>The game is inspired from amazing games like ISLANDERS and Dorfromantik. </p>",
